data.description: Discover the epitome of peaceful living in this meticulously cared for 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom sanctuary. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this home exudes warmth and comfort, having been lovingly maintained by its current owners. Step inside to be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, perfect for both daily living and entertaining guests. The recently painted white cabinets and luxury vinyl flooring elevate the space, offering a modern touch and a canvas for your personal style. Outside, escape to your private oasis. The backyard boasts a charming garden, ideal for cultivating your green thumb, while a secluded trail through the wooded area beckons for exploration and tranquility. Experience the harmony of nature and modern comforts in this cherished home. Your perfect retreat awaits.
